1.0.name: connect20/AT_Basic
1.0.description: AccurateTax Tax Tools - Basic version provides the capability for shoppers to have accurate sales tax calculated for their orders based on the storeowner's nexus. The system allows the shopper to enter either a 5-digit or zip+4 zipcode into their address information and will determine the correct sales tax rates based on that data.

suggest.magento-hackathon\/magento-composer-inst: Allows to manage this package as a dependency
